erifies** (no DB pollution). Patch staged: `patches/2026-06-21-C12-ctx-signals-verified-only.patch` (filter to `approval_state = 'verified'`; honest-labeling alt documented). **Positive in-window:** `1ceeddef` fixes a telegram intake **tenant-mislabel** (resolve by uploader user id, not the negative group chat id → no silent `MIRA_TENANT_ID` fallback). **If `MIRA_CTX_SIGNALS_ENABLED=1` is set on any deploy surface before the patch lands, re-grade C YELLOW.** Scorecard holds **4G/2Y/0R**. **Rotation Round 13 → D next.** All reads via `git show origin/main:`.) Beta-readiness == production == `origin/main`.
