| **8** | **Doc hygiene — `wiki/hot.md:233` migration head 037 vs actual 055 (Δ18, worsening)** | ⚪ orientation | OPEN | Founder note only (hot.md churns every session; a patch wouldn't stay clean). Authoritative head = `ls mira-hub/db/migrations \| tail -1`. The "session start: read hot.md" ritual mis-orients a beta agent. |

### Findings

| | Detail |
|---|---|
